The new chapter in the highly anticipated Elder Scrolls saga arrives from the makers of Game of the Year 2006 and 2008, Bethesda Game Studios. Skyrim reimagines and revolutionizes the open-world fantasy epic, bringing to life a complete virtual world open for you to explore any way you choose. Stirring spans the Empire of Tamriel. The High King of Skyrim has been murdered. As applicants come to the throne, are forming alliances. In the midst of this conflict, an ancient evil far more dangerous: Dragons, long lost to the passages of the Elder Scrolls, have returned to Tamriel. The future of Skyrim, even the Empire itself, hangs in the balance as they wait for the prophesized arrival of Dragon Born A endowed with the power of The Voice, the only one who can stand amongst the dragons hero.


Platform: PC
